name: Luprix - Beastmaster Strikeforce SE
description: #HENHalloween Special Edition. His friends call him Lu, his enemies call him Prix because he's kind of a dick. His friends think he's funny most of the time, the rest not so much but they don't live long to tell the tale. With an enchanted scythe capable of harnessing lunar energy he's able to generate deadly energy beams and is also an incredibly ferocious and agile fighter.
